            <h2>Group 2</h2>
            <p>Group two applies to verbs that end with -ити, іти or їти. This group, fortunately, has no sub-groups. Unfortunately, there are three different possible conjugations depending on the stem of the verb. For this group, we drop the last three letters of the verb rather than the last two. While the conjugation is different than group one, it is quite similar. Check the table below for the conjugations and some examples.</p>

